              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma-quanta single spectra from the",
                "145-Nd(n,inl+g) reaction were measured at angles",
                "of 90,110,125,135 and 148 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron beam was filtered to exclude thermal,",
                "resonance neutrons and gamma-radiation of the active",
                " core with the aid of 50 mm depleted metallic uranium,",
                "20mm boron carbide,1mm cadmium,10mm Pb and 6mm acrylic",
                "plastic. The diameter of the beam on the target was",
                "nearly 35mm."
              ]
